{"title":"Adidas launches clip-in version of Samba street shoe","link":"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/adidas-samba/","date":1614594173000,"content":"<img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Adidas-Velosamba-aacbdf0.jpg?quality=90&#038;resize=620,413\" srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Adidas-Velosamba-aacbdf0.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1440,959 1440w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Adidas-Velosamba-aacbdf0.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1200,799 1200w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Adidas-Velosamba-aacbdf0.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=960,639 960w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Adidas-Velosamba-aacbdf0.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=720,479 720w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Adidas-Velosamba-aacbdf0.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=576,383 576w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Adidas-Velosamba-aacbdf0.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=360,239 360w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Adidas-Velosamba-aacbdf0.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=180,119 180w, \" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" class=\"wp-image-620976 alignnone size-landscape_thumbnail\" alt=\"Adidas Velosamba urban cycling shoe\" title=\"Adidas Velosamba urban cycling shoe\" />                                            <p>Adidas has today released the Velosamba, a two-bolt clipless (clip-in) version of its Samba casual shoe, which is one of the most iconic shoes in streetwear.</p>\n<p>The shoe is the brand’s first ever cycling-specific casual shoe and comes hot on the heels of <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/adidas-the-road-shoe/\">The Road Shoe</a> launch in December.</p>\n<p>That shoe marked the brand’s overall re-entry into the cycling footwear market after a 15-year hiatus.</p>\n<h2>A classi