ality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Velosamba-05-5453e43.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=2222%2C1481 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Velosamba-05-5453e43.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Velosamba-05-5453e43.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Velosamba-05-5453e43.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Velosamba-05-5453e43.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=2222%2C1481 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img class=\"wp-image-620974 align size-landscape_thumbnail image-handler__image image-handler__image--aspect no-wrap js-lazyload\" data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/Velosamba-05-5453e43.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Adidas Velosamba\" title=\"Adidas Velosamba\"></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></picture></div><div class=\"caption-hold\"><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span class=\"caption-copy\"><i class=\"icon-arrow icon-camera-circle\"></i> The shoe is Adidas’s second cycling shoe launch in recent months.</span></figcaption><span class=\"im-image-caption\"> <i>Adidas</i></span></div>\n<p>The Velosamba is, in the brand’s words, “a recoding of an iconic Adidas silhouette into cycling”.</p>\n<p>Outwardly, you would be hard-pushed to tell it is even a cycling shoe – it really does look much like the classic Samba.</p>\n<p>Starting from the bottom up, the natural rubber outsole of the Velosamba is the same as found on the Samba, but the shoe features a full-length nylon insole to increase stiffness.</p>\n<p>The upper is made from a coated leather, which is said to be water-resistant.</p>\n<p>The three stripe pattern on the shoe – Adidas’s signature design – is made from a reflective material to improve low-light visibility.</p>\n<div class=\"image-handler__container image-handler__container--aspect\" style=\"padding-bottom: calc(100% / 1.501210653753);\">\n    <picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/velosamba-cream-310e9b3.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=299%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/velosamba-cream-310e9b3.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=599%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/velosamba-cream-310e9b3.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=899%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/velosamba-cream-310e9b3.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1199%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/velosamba-cream-310e9b3.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=299%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/velosamba-cream-310e9b3.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=599%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/velosamba-cream-310e9b3.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=899%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/velosamba-cream-310e9b3.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1199%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 375px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/velosamba-cream-310e9b3.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=354%2C236, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/velosamba-cream-310e9b3.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=708%2C472 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/product